-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-
Python "CPROPStoo" Implementation
-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-

Implementation of the signal-identification, object extraction, and
emission characterization package "cprops" in python.

--------------------
OVERALL STRUCTURE
--------------------

cube - defines a class to read and manipulate cubes.

mask - defines a class to create, manipulate, and read/write masks.

noise - defines a class to derive noise estimates

struct - helper class to build morphological structuring elements

--------------------
NEXT UP
--------------------

Up noise dimensionality, add visual feedback.

Error trap on CASA/astropy on load.

Implement CASA side.

Start testing on weird orders and degenerate axes.

Local maximum object.

Read on masks.

Read/write on noise.

